For these five years,

00:26:05.340 --> 00:26:06.740
everyone has been diligent
and dedicated.

00:26:07.300 --> 00:26:08.660
I've seen all your contributions

00:26:09.100 --> 00:26:10.340
to Tianlu.

00:26:11.420 --> 00:26:12.500
In the next five years,

00:26:13.140 --> 00:26:16.540
we will aim even higher.

00:26:17.060 --> 00:26:17.580
Alright.

