Old Sir is an elder from our village.

00:29:02.140 --> 00:29:04.860
He knows many things and has seen much.

00:29:04.980 --> 00:29:06.740
He's the one who told me about ballet.

00:29:08.220 --> 00:29:11.060
So you've never
learned ballet before, right?

00:29:14.380 --> 00:29:14.900
Then...

00:29:15.620 --> 00:29:17.420
Do you know what ballet is?

00:29:17.620 --> 00:29:19.100
It's dancing.

00:29:19.380 --> 00:29:21.100
It's different
from the dancing back home.

00:29:21.540 --> 00:29:23.740
I'm not sure why I want to learn it.

00:29:24.140 --> 00:29:26.540
Old Sir has some ballet magazines.

00:29:26.540 --> 00:29:29.340
I tried to copy the people
in the pictures, standing on my toes.

00:29:29.380 --> 00:29:31.220
When I stretch my arms and spin,

00:29:31.300 --> 00:29:33.220
it feels so free.

00:29:33.380 --> 00:29:35.620
It makes me happy. Old Sir is happy too.

00:29:36.060 --> 00:29:36.780
That's wonderful.

00:29:37.100 --> 00:29:38.460
We all understand

00:29:38.540 --> 00:29:39.860
Qu Zhen's situation now.

00:29:40.140 --> 00:29:40.740
Come on.

00:29:41.500 --> 00:29:42.340
Let's hear everyone's opinions.

