Fine for casual dancing.

00:30:21.340 --> 00:30:23.140
But I doubt

00:30:23.140 --> 00:30:24.620
she can make a career of it.

00:30:24.620 --> 00:30:25.460
It's just too difficult.

00:30:27.140 --> 00:30:28.620
I actually think this child

00:30:28.620 --> 00:30:29.740
has a better feel

00:30:30.500 --> 00:30:31.780
for ballet than most people.

00:30:34.060 --> 00:30:35.740
What is the purpose of dance?

00:30:36.340 --> 00:30:38.100
Must it always be about achievement?

00:30:38.980 --> 00:30:41.460
Can't liking it, finding joy in it,
enjoying it

00:30:41.940 --> 00:30:43.540
also be an achievement?

00:30:46.740 --> 00:30:47.420
Dab it.

